{"_id":"CWEWnhkru6aZyJr8","name":"Aganazzar's Scorcher","permission":{"default":0,"DJNYgTCLxATVgLjS":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A line of roaring flame 30 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d8 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</span></p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.&nbsp;</strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>","chat":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A line of roaring flame 30 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d8 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</span></p>\n<p><b>At Higher Levels.&nbsp;</b>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>\n                    \n                            <span class=\"components-blurb\">* - (a red dragon's scale)</span>","unidentified":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A line of roaring flame 30 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d8 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</span></p>\n<p><b>At Higher Levels.&nbsp;</b>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>\n                    \n                            <span class=\"components-blurb\">* - (a red dragon's scale)</span>"},"source":"EE 150","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":30,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"