{"_id":"PaYHvIdKa9eTpaXV","name":"Color Spray","permission":{"default":0,"DJNYgTCLxATVgLjS":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A dazzling array of flashing, colored light springs from your hand. Roll 6d10; the total is how many hit points of creatures this spell can affect. Creatures in a 15-foot cone originating from you are affected in ascending order of their current hit points (ignoring @Compendium[SharedData_Player.shared_journalCond.WYl3sSOLEez06WOG]{Unconscious} creatures and creatures that can't see).</p>\n<p>Starting with the creature that has the lowest current hit points, each creature affected by this spell is @Compendium[SharedData_Player.shared_journalCond.6Cvc68SOBbZQEAVz]{Blinded} until the end of your next turn. Subtract each creature's hit points from the total before moving on to the creature with the next lowest hit points. A creature's hit points must be equal to or less than the remaining total for that creature to be affected.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, roll an additional 2d10 for each slot level above 1st.</p>","chat":"<p>A dazzling array of flashing, colored light springs from your hand. Roll 6d10; the total is how many hit points of creatures this spell can affect. Creatures in a 15-foot cone originating from you are affected in ascending order of their current hit points (ignoring <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Unconscious\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/15-tooltip\">unconscious</a> creatures and creatures that can't see).</p>\n<p>Starting with the creature that has the lowest current hit points, each creature affected by this spell is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Blinded\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/1-tooltip\">blinded</a> until the&nbsp;end of your next turn. Subtract each creature's hit points from the total before moving on to the creature with the next lowest hit points. A creature's hit points must be equal to or less than the remaining total for that creature to be affected.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, roll an additional 2d10 for each slot level above 1st.</p>","unidentified":"<p>A dazzling array of flashing, colored light springs from your hand. Roll 6d10; the total is how many hit points of creatures this spell can affect. Creatures in a 15-foot cone originating from you are affected in ascending order of their current hit points (ignoring <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Unconscious\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/15-tooltip\">unconscious</a> creatures and creatures that can't see).</p>\n<p>Starting with the creature that has the lowest current hit points, each creature affected by this spell is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Blinded\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/1-tooltip\">blinded</a> until the&nbsp;end of your next turn. Subtract each creature's hit points from the total before moving on to the creature with the next lowest hit points. A creature's hit points must be equal to or less than the remaining total for that creature to be affected.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, roll an additional 2d10 for each slot level above 1st.</p>"},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":