tatistics. Some sample creatures are listed below.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the challenge rating increases by 1 for each slot level above 6th.<br><br></p>\n<p><strong>Sample Creatures</strong></p>\n<table class=\"summoning-creatures-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"table-challenge-rating-header\"><strong>CR</strong></th>\n<th class=\"table-creatures-name-header\"><strong>Creature Name</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>0</strong></td>\n<td><a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/frog\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16866-tooltip\">Frog</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/sea-horse\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/17009-tooltip\">Sea Horse</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/baboon\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16795-tooltip\">Baboon</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/badger\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16796-tooltip\">Badger</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/bat\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16802-tooltip\">Bat</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/cat\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16820-tooltip\">Cat</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/crab\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16833-tooltip\">Crab</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/deer\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/monsters/16839-tooltip\">Deer</a>, <a class=\"tooltip-hover monster-tooltip\" h