{"_id":"ZQvXSglTjEwWY5hB","name":"Life Transference","permission":{"default":0,"DJNYgTCLxATVgLjS":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You sacrifice some of your health to mend another creature&rsquo;s injuries. You take 4d8 necrotic damage, which can&rsquo;t be reduced in any way, and one creature of your choice that you can see within range regains a number of hit points equal to twice the necrotic damage you take.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\"><span class=\"Serif-Character-Style_Inline-Subhead-Serif\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong>&nbsp;</span>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>","chat":"<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\">You sacrifice some of your health to mend another creature&rsquo;s injuries. You take 4d8 necrotic damage, which can&rsquo;t be reduced in any way, and one creature of your choice that you can see within range regains a number of hit points equal to twice the necrotic damage you take.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Core-Styles_Core-Body\"><span class=\"Serif-Character-Style_Inline-Subhead-Serif\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong>&nbsp;</span>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>","unidentified":""},"source":"XGtE 160","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["4d8","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":fa