inst your spell save DC or be <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Frightened\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/5-tooltip?disable-webm=1&amp;disable-webm=1\">frightened</a> of the undead until the end of the target’s next turn.</p>\n<p class=\"Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body\"><em><strong>Grave Bolt (Skeletal Only).</strong> Ranged Spell Attack:</em> +3 + the spell’s level to hit, range 150 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 2d8 + 3 + the spell’s level necrotic damage.</p>\n<p class=\"Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body\"><em><strong>Rotting Claw (Putrid Only).</strong> Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +3 + the spell’s level to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 1d6 + 3 + the spell’s level slashing damage. If the target is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/11-tooltip?disable-webm=1&amp;disable-webm=1\">poisoned</a>, it must succeed on a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC or be <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Paralyzed\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/9-tooltip?disable-webm=1&amp;disable-webm=1\">paralyzed</a> until the end of its next turn.</p>\n</div>\n                    \n                            <span class=\"components-blurb\">* - (a gilded humanoid skull worth at least 300 gp)</span>"},"source":"Unearthed Arcana","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":90,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","act