{"_id":"pK0AqRwS0rkrGwu7","name":"Greater Invisibility","permission":{"default":0,"DJNYgTCLxATVgLjS":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You or a creature you touch becomes <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> until the spell ends. Anything the target is wearing or carrying is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> as long as it is on the target's person.</p>","chat":"<p>You or a creature you touch becomes <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> until the spell ends. Anything the target is wearing or carrying is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> as long as it is on the target's person.</p>","unidentified":"<p>You or a creature you touch becomes <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> until the spell ends. Anything the target is wearing or carrying is <a class=\"tooltip-hover condition-tooltip\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible\" data-tooltip-href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/conditions/8-tooltip\">invisible</a> as long as it is on the target's person.</p>"},"source":"","activati